flavorText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "94B98595460A59AB1426EF96F149C42A", "The minotaur have seized the ruins of Thanalus and I\'ve made an alliance with the leader of the Highwaymen. Glogora has warmed over! According to the Highwayman, the bandit king, the minotaur are after the Seeds of Eranthia, the essence infused seeds from the enchanted foret of the ancient Pyrians. I must find a way to infiltrate the ruins and retrieve the seeds before the minotaur claim them for whoever or whatever pulls their strings. ")
